Problem Name: Number of Workers by Department Starting in April or Later
Problem ID: 9847
Company: Ammazon
Difficulty Level: Easy
Link to Problem: https://platform.stratascratch.com/coding/9847-find-the-number-of-workers-by-department?code_type=1
Interview Date: NA

Problem: 
Find the number of workers by department who joined in or after April.

Output the department name along with the corresponding number of workers.

Sort records based on the number of workers in descending order.
My Code: 
select department, count(*) as num_workers 
from worker
where joining_date >= '2014-04-01'
group by 1;
